{
  "stem": "4113.3",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We wanted to know what it's going to be.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "He said, you are going to stay.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So we went back.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We didn't trust him.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "You know.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So what we did is we hid my sister and my little brother and my mother-- we hid them in the attic.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And my cousin hid their parents.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And we hid a number of people, you know, that we knew that can survive.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "You know, that they are-- they are at risk, at greater risk than we were.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And we went out to the cattle market.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "At the cattle market, there were all the Jews from our town plus many Jews that were resettled from areas in the West that the Germans took over and annexed as part of Germany from Warthegau from Litzmannstadt, which was [?",
      "word_count": 41
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "Luck. ?] There were many in our town, because they have to be resettled.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "So the-- the ghetto, the Jews, the numbers grew.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "Also the Jews from the little towns and the villages, from the shtetles, surrounding it all had to leave everything there and come in-- into our town.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "See, what they're trying-- what they were trying to do is conglomerate them in one spot so they are easy to be handled rather than have to go from village to village to get the Jews.",
      "word_count": 36
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And there were many Jews in the villages.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "If you saw the movie you know, this is how they were.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "They owned a tavern or they owned a little pension, [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "Or they had a cow and a few chickens.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And they would sell milk, kosher milk, et cetera.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So in the villages, there were Jews and in the tiny towns.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And they all had to come in.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So we now, you know, exploded with people.",
      "word_count": 8
    }
  ],
